{"tid":2007390,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民鄭錦滿：「立會事實處」明顯是泛民製作的網站，黃絲泛民抹黑熱狗為「建制派B隊」。","createTime":"2020-05-08T10:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T12:10:31.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e82905e62d06801e0964da37493b0e69563b296e","tid":2007390,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:05:10.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿：<br />\n「立會事實處」（ <a href=\"https://legco2020.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegco2020.com%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=a09aec19\" target=\"_blank\">https://legco2020.com/</a> ）明顯是泛民製作的網站，素材取自 Google 新聞、選舉事務處、立法會公開數據、政府統計處等資料去整合各立法會議員的投票紀錄。<br />\n黃絲講求 fact check ，又會鬥黃，以立法會投票紀錄作事實根據去分析的話，熱血公民主席鄭松泰議員與一眾保皇黨距離最遠，位列「光譜」最極端。以黃絲語言來講，就是「黃到發金」，但泛民 propaganda 偏偏抹黑熱狗為「建制派B隊」。<br />\n2016年之前熱血公民並沒有議席，對於拒絕思考的泛民支持者來講，這些卑劣的誣蔑無擬是有效的手段￼，令很多人對熱血公民有誤解。現在，愈來愈多人認為凡事需要 FC ，要講事實，那就請大家透過這些方便的工具去查核各立法會議員的工作吧。<br />\n對於想更了解熱血公民作為「本土自由派的定位」的各位，請收看第1328集《熱血政治》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XRi7oN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XRi7oN.jpg&h=0617d575&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f794c999019ffc9960c7e48caf9c7de8121a7047","tid":2007390,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"明白晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以更加唔會投熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570d13eac6998f7dcfd2b22e58374b007f59da8b","tid":2007390,"uid":68926,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"我支持熱血公民<br />\n所以會投佢地白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faa4bc45521dc9004