":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"以子之矛，高<br />\n熱狗：白票兵言論不代我，學教主話齋有本事斬撚死佢，唔好搞我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfL0BZi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfL0BZi.png&h=f6682fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"選完之後就講：<br />\n<br />\n【熱普城三個撚樣】<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達：香港選民係仆街冚街鏟，你嗰區得泛民同建制，一定係投建制，選前我緊係唔講，費事影響熱血公民，<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民：畀你過半數又點，呢個唔係一個公投，邊個講血債票償就唔好投佢，投白票投廢票。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：有本土投本土，冇本土投建制，加倍懲罰泛民。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭錦滿，又老屈連燈投建制。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1755805/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1755805/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n黃洋達 : 要消滅泛民, 因為香港選民係仆街陷家鏟既賤人! 要推和理非去食彈食tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1755902/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1755902/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n熱血公民:望參加「初選」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1975107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1975107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［罷投］黃毓民：我不會投票！ 警告勇武派與泛民團結：條路自己揀，仆街唔好喊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753472</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/833142083471222/permalink/2993267324125343/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F833142083471222%2Fpermalink%2F2993267324125343%2F&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=d9b240fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/833142083471222/permalink/2993267324125343/</a>"}]}